<template><AdminTablePage title="岗位审核" desc="审核企业发布岗位，驳回不合规岗位或下架违规岗位" :list="list" :total="total" :loading="loading" :query="query" :show-add="false" @load="load" :action-width="240"><template #toolbar><el-input v-model="query.title" placeholder="岗位名称" clearable style="width:220px"/><el-select v-model="query.auditStatus" clearable placeholder="审核状态" style="width:140px"><el-option label="待审核" :value="0"/><el-option label="通过" :value="1"/><el-option label="驳回" :value="2"/></el-select><el-button type="primary" @click="reload">查询</el-button></template><template #columns><el-table-column prop="title" label="岗位" min-width="170"/><el-table-column prop="companyName" label="企业" min-width="170"/><el-table-column prop="city" label="城市" width="90"/><el-table-column label="薪资" width="120"><template #default="{row}"><span style="color:#f56c6c">{{row.salaryMin}}-{{row.salaryMax}}K</span></template></el-table-column><el-table-column label="审核" width="100"><template #default="{row}"><el-tag :type="row.auditStatus===1?'success':row.auditStatus===2?'danger':'warning'">{{['待审核','通过','驳回'][row.auditStatus]}}</el-tag></template></el-table-column><el-table-column prop="auditRemark" label="审核意见" min-width="150" show-overflow-tooltip/></template><template #rowActions="{row}"><el-button text type="success" @click="audit(row,1)">通过</el-button><el-button text type="danger" @click="openReject(row)">驳回</el-button><el-button text type="warning" @click="offline(row)">下架</el-button></template><template #dialogs><el-dialog v-model="dialog" title="驳回岗位" width="480px"><el-input v-model="remark" type="textarea" :rows="4" placeholder="请输入驳回原因"/><template #footer><el-button @click="dialog=false">取消</el-button><el-button type="danger" @click="reject">确认驳回</el-button></template></el-dialog></template></AdminTablePage></template><script setup>import{reactive,ref,onMounted}from'vue';import{ElMessage,ElMessageBox}from'element-plus';import AdminTablePage from '@/components/AdminTablePage.vue';import{adminApi}from'@/api';const query=reactive({pageNum:1,pageSize:10,title:'',auditStatus:''});const list=ref([]),total=ref(0),loading=ref(false),dialog=ref(false),current=ref(null),remark=ref('');const load=async()=>{loading.value=true;try{const p={...query};if(p.auditStatus==='')delete p.auditStatus;const r=await adminApi.jobAuditList(p);list.value=r.data.records;total.value=Number(r.data.total)}finally{loading.value=false}};const reload=()=>{query.pageNum=1;load()};const audit=async(row,status)=>{await adminApi.auditJob(row.id,status,'');ElMessage.success('审核通过');load()};const openReject=row=>{current.value=row;remark.value='';dialog.value=true};const reject=async()=>{await adminApi.auditJob(current.value.id,2,remark.value);ElMessage.success('已驳回');dialog.value=false;load()};const offline=row=>ElMessageBox.confirm('确定下架该岗位？').then(async()=>{await adminApi.offlineJob(row.id);ElMessage.success('已下架');load()});onMounted(load)</script>